snippet.title: Learn Chess with Chess Tools - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Game on steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2741350/Chess_Tools/

Recently released, Chess Tools is a new way to learn chess with tools that show you information directly on the board. With many tutorials and famous games to help you learn.
